#!/bin/ksh
#!/bin/zsh 
##
## [3] USP
##         ("> ")name, emailplacehow
##         /home/usp/members.csvCSV1
##         
## 
##         > USP
##         > 
##         > XXXXXXXX
##         > ---       ()
##         > name=              4
##         > email=xxx@usptomonokai.jp  
##         > place=               
##         > how=twitter                
##         > ---
##
tail -n5 |sort -r |while read -r l;do set -- "$@" "${l#*=}"; done; print -r "$2,$4,$1,$3" >>/home/usp/members.csv
